"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:10.5.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">10.5.1</span> 标题：耳环、鼻环（earring, nose ring）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：נֶזֶם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：nezem)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:22\">GEN 24:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:30\">GEN 24:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:47\">GEN 24:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:4\">GEN 35:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:2\">EXO 32:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:3\">EXO 32:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:22\">EXO 35:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:24\">JDG 8:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:24\">JDG 8:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:25\">JDG 8:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:26\">JDG 8:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:11\">JOB 42:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:22\">PRO 11:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:12\">PRO 25:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:21\">ISA 3:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:12\">EZK 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:15\">HOS 2:15</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עָגִיל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘agil)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:50\">NUM 31:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:12\">EZK 16:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἐνώτιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：enōtion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:4\">JDT 10:4</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0531_earrings_gold.jpg\" alt=\"金耳环\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">金耳环 (Metropolitan Museum of Art, Public domain, MMA)</figcaption></figure>耳环和鼻环是分别戴在耳朵和鼻子上的小环状饰物，通常用银或金做成，上面或多或少都有一些精致的装饰。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>希伯来文<em>nezem</em> 指戴在耳朵或鼻子上的环，是一种装饰性的珠宝。</p>\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/UBS-0037_nose_ring.jpg\" alt=\"鼻环\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">鼻环 (© Deutsche Bibelgesellschaft, Stuttgart by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:12\">EZK 16:12</a> 中，希伯来文<em>‘agil</em> 明显指耳环，在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:50\">NUM 31:50</a> 中也可能是指耳环。</p>\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0071_head_of_woman_with_earrings.png\" alt=\"OAI-0071_head_of_woman_with_earrings\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\"> (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:4\">JDT 10:4</a> 中，希腊文<em>enōtion</em> 特指耳环。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
